'''''silmë''''' is a noun meaning "starlight" in [[Quenya]].<ref name="Names">{{App|Letters}}, Note, ''The names of the letters''</ref>

[[Image:Silme.gif|left]]''Silmë'' is also the name in Quenya of the twenty-ninth letter of the [[Tengwar]] alphabet.<ref name="Names"/>  In all modes this letter represents '''S'''.<ref>{{App|Letters}}, Note, ''The additional letters''</ref> The Westron name for this letter is '''''Só'''''.<ref>See ''[[Alphabet of Fëanor: Numenian, or Westron, Mode]]''</ref>


<!-- An extra blank line is added to prevent the Etymology section title from being indented. -->
==Etymology==
The word derives from the [[Primitive Quendian]] [[Sundocarme|root]] [[SIL]].<ref>{{LR|Etymologies}}, SIL -</ref>
